<td class="mbox-text" style=""><a href="/wiki/Wikinews" title="Wikinews">Wikinews</a> has related news: <i><b><a href="http://en.wikinews.org/wiki/Interview_with_gay_marriage_movement_founder_Evan_Wolfson" class="extiw" title="wikinews:Interview with gay marriage movement founder Evan Wolfson">Interview with gay marriage movement founder Evan Wolfson</a></b></i></td>
