<li id="cite_note-161"><b><a href="#cite_ref-161" title="">^</a></b> Szymanski, Dawn M.; Carr, Erika R. "The roles of gender role conflict and internalized heterosexism in gay and bisexual men's psychological distress: Testing two mediation models." <i>Psychology of Men &amp; Masculinity,</i> Vol 9(1), Jan 2008, 40-54.</li>
<li id="cite_note-162"><b><a href="#cite_ref-162" title="">^</a></b> Price, M. "UPFRONT - Research uncovers the stress created by same-sex marriage bans" in <i>Monitor on Psychology</i>, Volume 40, No. 1, page 10, January 2009. Washington DC: American Psychological Association. <a href="http://www.apa.org/monitor/2009/01/marriage-bans.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.apa.org/monitor/2009/01/marriage-bans.html" rel="nofollow">[8]</a></li>
