<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;">Nationwide</div>
</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;padding:0.35em 0; line-height:1.3em;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_the_Netherlands" title="Same-sex marriage in the Netherlands">Netherlands</a> <small>(since 2001)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Belgium" title="Same-sex marriage in Belgium">Belgium</a> <small>(since 2003)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Spain" title="Same-sex marriage in Spain">Spain</a> <small>(since 2005)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Canada" title="Same-sex marriage in Canada">Canada</a> <small>(since 2005)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_South_Africa" title="Same-sex marriage in South Africa">South Africa</a> <small>(since 2006)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Norway" title="Same-sex marriage in Norway">Norway</a> <small>(since 2009)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Sweden" title="Same-sex marriage in Sweden">Sweden</a> <small>(commencing 2009-05)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Nepal" title="Same-sex marriage in Nepal">Nepal</a> <small>(expected 2010)</small></span></div>
