ki/Domestic_partnership_in_Maine" title="Domestic partnership in Maine">Maine</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Maryland" title="Same-sex marriage in Maryland" class="mw-redirect">Maryland</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Minnesota" title="Same-sex marriage in Minnesota">Minnesota</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_New_Hampshire" title="Same-sex marriage in New Hampshire" class="mw-redirect">New Hampshire</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_New_Jersey" title="Same-sex marriage in New Jersey" class="mw-redirect">New Jersey</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_New_York" title="Same-sex marriage in New York">New York</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Rhode_Island" title="Same-sex marriage in Rhode Island">Rhode Island</a>, <a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_Vermont" title="Same-sex marriage in Vermont">Vermont</a></small>)</span></div>
